{"tid":2004930,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"何文田屋苑外擲汽油彈 撒百張傳單追債","createTime":"2020-05-06T18:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T19:50:51.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"07e0288292cfcd748904777fcdcf08d2075d203c","tid":2004930,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T18:58:32.000Z","msg":"何文田衛理道18號君頤峰，凌晨零時許，一輛私家車駛至屋苑門外，一名男子下車拋擲2個汽油彈，及將大批印有追債字句A4單張撒落地上，隨即登回私家車逃去無蹤，汽油彈跌在屋苑對開行人路花槽旁邊，一度發出火光。<br />\n<br />\n消防員接報趕至現場，發現花槽被火熏黑，地上佈滿玻璃樽碎片，認為起火原因有可疑。警員封鎖現場展開調查，並撿獲約100張追債A4紙。"},{"pid":"db13ca5ab0ee858a69b798c04380e7647f088ab5","tid":2004930,"uid":273791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:00:36.000Z","msg":"又入我哋數lu"},{"pid":"cf83e629b7d3ebd411ca0bd111f009775bb173d0","tid":2004930,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:06:16.000Z","msg":"汽油師! 不割!!"},{"pid":"5ad8f8fd2c2bbdf6792ba8f66e52a568221e7f70","tid":2004930,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:28:40.000Z","msg":"日頭追數，夜晚抗爭，手足嚟自各行各業"},{"pid":"87bcea8f90f51935dd62dc65d6eba0a51d9e6ff8","tid":2004930,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:41:50.000Z","msg":"又幾利落"},{"pid":"44ad14760fe0f7eb62aea9f4ee4f4fb73889f596","tid":2004930,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:50:51.000Z","msg":"火魔已代替淋紅油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}